premise_source_doc_sentence: Charles ' second wife , from 1363 , was Helena Israelsdotter of Finsta , who died 1375 at latest , daughter of Israel Birgersson of Finsta , PC , last male of Finsta family , justiciar of Uppland , and Helena was sister of Charles ' first cousin Philip Nielson of Salsta 's wife Ramborg Israelsdotter of Finsta .
